遊戲發售三天內共售出超过350万份<ref>{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy 7 Remake launch numbers broke 3.5 million in first 3 days |url=https://www.gamesradar.com/final-fantasy-7-remake-launch-numbers-broke-35-million-in-first-3-days/ |date=2020-04-21 |accessdate=2020-04-25 |last=Sheridan |first=Connor |work=[[GamesRadar+|GamesRadar+]] |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200425161558/https://www.gamesradar.com/final-fantasy-7-remake-launch-numbers-broke-35-million-in-first-3-days/ |archivedate=2020-04-25}}</ref>，超过2018年《[[蜘蛛俠_(2018年遊戲)|蜘蛛俠]]》（330万）創下的銷售紀錄<ref>{{cite tweet|user=PlayStation |number=1042775621074669568 |date=2018-09-20 |title=Marvel's Spider-Man is setting records! It's now the fastest-selling first-party PlayStation title, selling 3.3M+ in its first 3 days. Thanks to all the fans, and congrats to @InsomniacGames & @MarvelGames! #SpiderManPS4|language=en|accessdate=2018-09-22|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180922034331/https:/twitter.com/PlayStation/status/1042775621074669568|archivedate=2018-09-22}}</ref>，是PlayStation 4游戏中最熱銷的遊戲，也是历史上首周销量最高的PlayStation 4游戏之一。《最终幻想VII 重制版》打進多國/區域周銷量排行榜，獲得日本、台灣、韓國、英國、意大利、法國冠軍寶座<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=195672 |title=MediaCreate 4 月 6 日～4 月 12 日一週銷售排行榜 《FF VII 重製版》席捲日台韓銷售榜 |author=Sam |publisher=[[巴哈姆特電玩資訊站|巴哈姆特電玩資訊站]] |date=2020-04-20 |accessdate=2020-06-30 |language=zh |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200630182550/https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=195672 |archivedate=2020-06-30 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=UK Charts: Final Fantasy 7 Remake is No.1 as boxed market grows again |url=https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2020-04-12-uk-charts-final-fantasy-vii-remake-is-no-1-as-boxed-market-grows-again |date=2020-04-12 |accessdate=2020-06-30 |first=Christopher |last=Dring |work=GamesIndustry.biz |language=en |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200416080415/https://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/2020-04-12-uk-charts-final-fantasy-vii-remake-is-no-1-as-boxed-market-grows-again |archivedate=2020-04-16}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ilvideogioco.com/2020/04/20/classifiche-italiane-final-fantasy-vii-remake-e-in-vetta/ |script-title=it:Classifiche italiane, Final Fantasy VII Remake è in vetta |last=Ullo |first=Edoardo |publisher=IlVideogioco |date=2020-04-20 |accessdate=2020-06-30 |language=it |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200630184330/https://www.ilvideogioco.com/2020/04/20/classifiche-italiane-final-fantasy-vii-remake-e-in-vetta/ |archivedate=2020-06-30 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.jeuxvideo.com/news/1214300/ventes-de-jeux-en-france-semaine-15-final-fantasy-vii-peut-il-detroner-animal-crossing.htm |script-title=fr:Ventes de jeux en France : Semaine 15 - Final Fantasy VII peut-il détrôner Animal Crossing ? |publisher=[[Jeuxvideo.com|Jeuxvideo.com]] |date=2020-04-20 |accessdate= |language=fr |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200625143957/http://www.jeuxvideo.com/news/1214300/ventes-de-jeux-en-france-semaine-15-final-fantasy-vii-peut-il-2020-06-25detroner-animal-crossing.htm |archivedate=2020-06-25}}</ref>。發售約4個月後，PS4版遊戲的銷量超了500萬套<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=201452 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2021-11-13 |archive-date=2021-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211113032126/https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/detail.php?sn=201452 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

根據[[法米通|法米通]]的統計，《最终幻想VII 重制版》在日本发售首周末售出702,853份实体版<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.famitsu.com/news/202004/16196823.html |script-title=ja:【ソフト＆ハード週間販売数】『FF7 リメイク』が70.3万本で1位！ PS4＆PS4 Proも合計7.9万台と大幅増【4/6～4/12】 |publisher=[[ファミ通.com|ファミ通.com]] |date=2020-04-16 |accessdate=2020-04-17 |language=ja |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200417010511/https://www.famitsu.com/news/202004/16196823.html |archivedate=2020-04-17 }}</ref>，并且许多商店售罄<ref>{{Cite web|title=FF7 Remake well received in Japan despite lockdown – but Switch hardware sales plunge as supply tightens {{!}} Business News|url=https://www.mcvuk.com/business-news/ff7-remake-well-received-in-japan-despite-lockdown-but-switch-hardware-sales-plunge-as-supply-tightens/|accessdate=2020-06-30|date=2020-04-20|work=MCV/DEVELOP|language=en-GB|archive-date=2021-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109054222/https://www.mcvuk.com/business-news/ff7-remake-well-received-in-japan-despite-lockdown-but-switch-hardware-sales-plunge-as-supply-tightens/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。包括数字版在内，发售三天内日本市场销量超过100万份<ref>{{Cite web |script-title=ja:"『FF7 リメイク』発売3日で世界販売本数350万本突破！ 日本国内でも100万本以上を売り上げ" |url=https://www.famitsu.com/news/202004/21197153.html |accessdate=2020-04-21 |publisher=[[ファミ通.com|ファミ通.com]] |language=ja |archive-date=2020-04-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200422202200/https://www.famitsu.com/news/202004/21197153.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在英国，其首周末的銷量預計售出60,000份实体版<ref>{{Cite web |title=Final Fantasy VII Remake Fares Admirably at UK Retail Amid Coronavirus Crisis |url=https://www.pushsquare.com/news/2020/04/final_fantasy_vii_remake_fares_admirably_at_uk_retail_amid_coronavirus_crisis |accessdate=2020-06-30 |date=2020-04-12 |last=Barker |first=Sammy |work=Push Square |language=en-GB |archive-date=2021-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210223063003/https://www.pushsquare.com/news/2020/04/final_fantasy_vii_remake_fares_admirably_at_uk_retail_amid_coronavirus_crisis |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在北美，重制版是2020年4月最畅销的游戏。它成为史上销售最快的《最终幻想》系列游戏，超过了《[[最終幻想XV|最終幻想XV]]》之前创造的发行记录<ref>{{Citation|title=Final Fantasy 7 Remake Is April 2020's Best-Selling Game, Sets Franchise Record - IGN|url=https://www.ign.com/articles/final-fantasy-7-remake-is-best-selling-game-of-april-2020-sets-franchise-record|accessdate=2020-06-30|language=en|archive-date=2020-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200522164858/https://www.ign.com/articles/final-fantasy-7-remake-is-best-selling-game-of-april-2020-sets-franchise-record|dead-url=no}}</ref>，并且是2020年4月美国下载次数最多的PlayStation 4游戏<ref name=":7">{{Cite web|title=Final Fantasy 7 Remake Was Best Selling US PlayStation Store Game|url=https://www.siliconera.com/final-fantasy-7-remake-playstation-store-sales-april-2020/|accessdate=2020-06-30|date=2020-05-07|work=Siliconera|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200509063625/https://www.siliconera.com/final-fantasy-7-remake-playstation-store-sales-april-2020/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。德国贸易协会GAME宣布，《最终幻想VII 重制版》仅用了几天时间就在德国售出10万多套，获得了金牌销售奖<ref>{{Cite web |script-title=de:Glorreiche Rückkehr: game Sales Award für FINAL FANTASY VII Remake |url=https://www.game.de/glorreiche-rueckkehr-game-sales-award-fuer-final-fantasy-vii-remake/ |accessdate=2020-06-30 |date=2020-04-15 |first=Martin |last=Puppe |work=game |language=de |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200630185932/https://www.game.de/glorreiche-rueckkehr-game-sales-award-fuer-final-fantasy-vii-remake/ |archivedate=2020-06-30 }}</ref>，也是4月第二賣座的遊戲<ref>{{Cite web |script-title=de:Top 20 PC & Konsole – April 2020 |url=https://www.game.de/marktdaten/top-20-pc-konsole-april-2020/ |accessdate=2020-06-30 |first=Thorsten |last=Hamdorf |work=game |language=de |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20200630185713/https://www.game.de/marktdaten/top-20-pc-konsole-april-2020/ |archivedate=2020-06-30 }}</ref>。重制版也是2020年4月在欧洲下载量排名第四的PlayStation 4游戏<ref name=":7" />。

== 奖项 ==
在游戏发售前，《最终幻想VII 重制版》获得了2019年[[E3电子娱乐展|E3]]展会最佳游戏展示奖。<ref name="#5"/>

在游戏发布后，游戏获得了PlayStation编辑选择奖。<ref name="#6"/>在2020年度的[[游戏大奖|游戏大奖]]中，一共获得包括「年度游戏」在内的6项提名，最终拿下「最佳角色扮演遊戲」及「最佳配樂／原聲帶」兩部門獎項。在第24届[[D.I.C.E.大奖|D.I.C.E大奖]]中，获得「年度角色扮演遊戲」奖项。<ref>{{Cite web|title=D.I.C.E大奖结果公开：《黑帝斯》夺年度游戏 - vgtime.com|url=https://www.vgtime.com/topic/1120985.jhtml|accessdate=2021-04-28|work=VGTime|language=zh-cn|archive-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430055126/https://www.vgtime.com/topic/1120985.jhtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

